Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:18.88,SeriesTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334.133,309.733)\fad(150,270)}Brave{\fscx900} {\r}Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:24.55,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Over a million of them shine with a blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:31.23,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The shards of love have scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:38.23,SongOP,,0,0,0,,It's brewing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:41.19,SongOP,,0,0,0,,A storm that you'll confront
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:44.74,SongOP,,0,0,0,,And because I believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:49.66,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.87,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.29,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Courage and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:03.34,SongOP,,0,0,0,,That moment when we join our strength GATHER WAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:06.89,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:10.26,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'd almost forgotten it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:18.61,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The fiery burning and important PASSIONATE feeling in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious and vast universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In this universe exists the evil life forms, \Nthe space pirates Geisters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,who've invaded Earth in order to obtain the treasures of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in front of the Geisters who use destruction and plunder as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a hero appeared, who completely stood in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the cosmic police, Exkaiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of Brave Exkaiser and his friends, who fight against evil all around the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:18.83,EpisodeTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328.02,393.2)}Great Adventure at the Pyramids
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there supposed to be no treasure here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No... There is something here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've forgotten that \Nmysterious incident on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Kaisers' secret is hidden in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dino Gest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a map!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ How many nights to sleep before it's New Year's... ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ At New Year's we eat mochi... ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dino Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Open that stone coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you looking, Ptera?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're ancient letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"We'll leave behind the power of justice \Nfor the one who comes later."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the cosmic policemen that once visited this planet left here an Life Energy Capture Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Life Energy Capture Device!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we have this, we can seal \Naway those Kaisers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But this alone isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We need an Emerald Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable that she won the first prize trip \Nto Egypt in a lottery...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family's mama is way too lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! This is at Hoshikawa's!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief editor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokuda-kun, thanks for looking after the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama has something to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam has?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tokuda, have you given Mario food properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please have no worries about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done a perfect job on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my New Year's meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's Mario's New Year's meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop here, Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't climb anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an amazing place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that humans built these\N over 4000 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe aliens actually built them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as unscientific as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,These pyramids were built by numerous slaves, \Nand it took over 20 years to complete them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kouta had lived during that time, you would've\N most likely been put to work as a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd watch the first sunrise \Nof New Year from the pyramid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Young sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a phone call from boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, when will you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want to see you, papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Young sir had made promises \Nto meet his father here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But he suddenly had to go to Europe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of their business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even care about my papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Young sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the New Year's gift from boss to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to give it on New Year's Day, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,New Year's gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The top-notch men are always lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun is trying to act tough, \Nbut I'm sure he's actually lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just something I want\N to ask from you, Exkaiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend is feeling down because of his family,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but that friend doesn't want others \Nto be involved in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're true friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no need to be awkward and\N just say out loud what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're true friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's trouble, Kouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun isn't in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser! Let's talk again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Geisters appeared again at the Kusunoki village's ancient tomb last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They dug up the ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they targeting this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the cache of the Emerald Stone\N that Lord Dino Geist mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, time to get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who on earth built such a big pyramid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to retrieve the New Year's \Ngift that he threw away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he's acting tough,\N Takumi really loves his father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just a sphinx...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bother! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We must escape, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Geister appeared at the pyramid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! I'll come immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta! I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should inform Lord \NDino Geist about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If some other people come, smash them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Takumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared... I'm so scared, papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Spare my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because you two came\Nthat we fell to this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Such thing is rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for you to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're true friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no need to be awkward and\N just say out loud what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a king's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be that we found a new \Nroom in this pyramid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Takumi-kun went...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kouta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi is so selfish that there's no helping him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why his father won't even see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to be his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you would \Nunderstand my feelings!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I would understand \Nthe feelings of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who easily throws away the New Year's gift\N that his father especially got for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I do understand your\N feelings of retrieving this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, we must hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that the \NEmerald Stone is in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The shield shone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a proof that it's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found the Emerald Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Emerald Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we have this, we can \Nimprison those guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to fear Exkaiser anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He can imprison Exkaiser with this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi, lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let Geisters have this Emerald Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We must take it and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi, Kotomi-chan... Let's lift it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This suit is made in Italy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be the ones to let \Ngo of the Emerald Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No way we'll let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit! They escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must I end up in a situation like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit is close! Hang in there, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Impact Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're alright, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Another hindrance appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have the pyramid's treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The pyramid's treasures? Looks \Nlike you don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Crush him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Breast Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Fusion, Dragon Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should power up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rocket Cluster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My New Year's gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have this, you bastards\N won't be bothering us anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That went well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an Life Energy Capture Device \Nthat your ancestors left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back the Emerald Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave the rest to that guy and retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,King Loader!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Giant Fusion, Great Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Tomahawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's play catch together with this ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to make as much time as \Npossible for that. Regards, father."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Geisters have appeared once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The sphinx has disappeared from Egypt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sphinx?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's interview the eye-witnesses now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun? Kotomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Thanks for the New Year's gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... What about the sphinx...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokuda, are you watching? It's a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give Mario food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit early, but Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Chief editor, madam... and also Fuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser fixed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Geisters stole that weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was something that Exkaiser's \Nancestors had left behind on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Life Energy Capture Device, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like things will get troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:56.20,SongED,,0,0,0,,Faraway wind carries your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:05.29,SongED,,0,0,0,,What could you discover from this excited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:15.34,SongED,,0,0,0,,Dreams get bigger strongly and fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:22.97,SongED,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to be who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:31.27,SongED,,0,0,0,,Embrace your enthusiastic heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:39.28,SongED,,0,0,0,,And try walking that path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:46.28,NextEpisodePreview,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323.74,314.667)}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure that Exkaiser's ancestors had left\N behind was taken away by Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like something awful will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone of Kaisers, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino Geist is waiting in ambush at the oil platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible! God Max is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Brave Exkaiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Oil Platform Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,3 episodes left until Geisters get arrested!
